body: Though I’m not 100% sure. It kinda looks like she calls the dog darling at the end. But it could be that she’s calling darling to her boyfriend to begin their sex play as he watches from the bushes.

Fascinating read. Very messed up, but somehow straddling the line where it’s not incomprehensible. @smelly_armpits_boy it’s the boyfriend. She calls him darling when asked if he’s a suitable enough man at the end. Fascinating how at the end, the boyfriend turned out to be perhaps the most messed up one.
